text: Gerrish-Higgins School District serves 1750 students in a area in Roscommon County, Michigan. It consists of two elementary schools, a middle school, and a high school. == School Board == *Superintendent: Dr. Millie Park Mellgren == Schools == *Roscommon High School *Roscommon Middle School *Roscommon Elementary School *St. Helen Elementary School Category:School districts in Michigan Category:Education in Roscommon County, Michigan
